data.summary: [PR Newswire] - Allot Communications Ltd. (NASDAQ: ALLT, TASE: ALLT) (the "Company" or "we"), a leading global provider of security and monetization solutions that enable service providers to protect and personalize the digital experience, today announces the appointment of Mr. Alberto Sessa as the Company's new Chief Financial Officer. Mr. Sessa will replace Mr. Shmuel Arvatz, Allot's current CFO, who is leaving to become the CFO of a privately-held company.
